664
00:38:39,039 --> 00:38:40,119
Well...

665
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:42,440
It's our job to help people.

666
00:38:43,119 --> 00:38:44,769
But the cost of repair...

667
00:38:45,119 --> 00:38:47,440
should be enough for you to buy a new twin brother.

668
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,809
Sir, get me the cheapest one.

669
00:38:58,809 --> 00:38:59,809
