670
00:38:59,809 --> 00:39:00,809
Can I try?

671
00:39:00,809 --> 00:39:02,679
- It's okay. - Can you slot the card in for me?

672
00:39:02,679 --> 00:39:03,809
- Can I try? - Okay.

673
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,000
Yes, you can.

674
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:06,920
Thank you.

675
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:09,239
I'm fine as long as the phone works.

676
00:39:09,239 --> 00:39:10,400
It's too expensive.

677
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,480
Most of them are glorious but not practical.

678
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,639
We should spend money wisely, right?

679
00:39:12,639 --> 00:39:13,809
Look at that.

680
00:39:13,809 --> 00:39:15,329
They all look the same,

681
00:39:15,329 --> 00:39:16,440
but that one is so expensive.

682
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,360
- Okay. - Thank you.

683
00:39:19,719 --> 00:39:21,329
That's good.

684
00:39:23,079 --> 00:39:24,639
WeChat is already installed on the phone, right?

685
00:39:24,639 --> 00:39:26,329
- It's all there. - Can I log in first?

686
00:39:26,329 --> 00:39:28,000
- Yes. - In case someone is looking for me.

687
00:39:28,329 --> 00:39:29,920
My phone has been wet for two days.

688
