696
00:39:56,289 --> 00:39:58,329
There is no need for courtesy. She doesn't care about you at all.

697
00:39:58,329 --> 00:39:59,559
Why are you taking it so seriously?

698
00:39:59,559 --> 00:40:00,559
I'll take a look.

699
00:40:00,559 --> 00:40:01,679
I'm upset.

700
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,519
Qian Qian...

701
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:10,880
