702
00:40:11,559 --> 00:40:13,079
Isn't this a villa with a sea view?

703
00:40:15,329 --> 00:40:17,719
I think my dad has a house there too.

704
00:40:18,809 --> 00:40:19,809
That's nice.

705
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,639
Did Qian Qin tell you who that man is?

706
00:40:25,119 --> 00:40:26,159
No.

707
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:28,769
I only know that he's her type.

708
00:40:31,559 --> 00:40:34,400
What if Hai Xing threatens to kill himself every day?

709
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,719
Qian Qian seems serious this time.

710
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:38,960
When this is all over,

711
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,119
Hai Xing will give up then.

